## ✅ Proper Project Structure

```text
Xai-governance-platform/
│
├── backend/
│   ├── app/
│   │   ├── main.py            # FastAPI Entry Point (CORS, Lifespan, Middleware)
│   │   ├── db/
│   │   │   ├── mongo.py       # Database Connection & Timeout Handling
│   │   ├── core/
│   │   │   ├── config.py      # Pydantic Settings & Env Loading
│   │   ├── api/
│   │   │   ├── routes/        # Feature Routes (Models, Governance, Chat, etc.)
│   ├── .env                   # Backend Environment Variables
│   ├── requirements.txt       # Python Dependencies (inc. python-dotenv)
│
├── frontend/
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── services/
│   │   │   ├── apiClient.js   # Centralized API Connection (Axios)
│   ├── .env                   # Frontend Environment (VITE_API_BASE_URL)
│   ├── package.json           # Node.js Dependencies
```

## ✅ Corrected Backend Code (Key Highlights)

### 📌 [backend/app/db/mongo.py](file:///c:/Users/Aarush/Documents/Anos/Xai-governance-platform/backend/app/db/mongo.py)
Updated with robust timeout handling and non-blocking connectivity checks.
```python
client = AsyncIOMotorClient(
    settings.mongodb_uri,
    serverSelectionTimeoutMS=5000,
    connectTimeoutMS=5000,
    socketTimeoutMS=5000
)

async def check_connection() -> bool:
    try:
        await get_client().admin.command('ping')
        return True
    except Exception:
        return False
```

### 📌 [backend/app/main.py](file:///c:/Users/Aarush/Documents/Anos/Xai-governance-platform/backend/app/main.py)
Optimized for developer experience with clear startup logs and fixed CORS logic.
```python
@asynccontextmanager
async def lifespan(_: FastAPI):
    # Non-blocking Database check
    db_connected = await check_connection()
    print(f"🚀 Server running on port: {settings.port}")
    print(f"{'✅ Database Connected' if db_connected else '❌ Database Connection Failed'}")
    
    if db_connected:
        asyncio.create_task(ensure_indexes()) # Background task
    yield
    await close_client()

# Outermost CORS Middleware (Handles Preflights Early)
app.add_middleware(
    CORSMiddleware,
    allow_origins=get_cors_origins(),
    allow_credentials=True,
    allow_methods=["*"],
    allow_headers=["*"],
)
```

## ✅ Required Commands to Run the Project

### 1. Backend Setup
```powershell
cd backend
# Enable virtual environment (if using)
.\venv\Scripts\activate
# Install all required packages
pip install -r requirements.txt
# Start the server (Live Reload enabled)
uvicorn app.main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000 --reload
```

### 2. Frontend Setup
```powershell
cd frontend
# Ensure dependencies are up to date
npm install
# Start Vite development server
npm run dev
```

---

> [!TIP]
> **Health Check**: Use `http://localhost:8000/health` to verify system status at any time. If the database shows `disconnected`, verify your `MONGODB_URI` in [backend/.env](file:///c:/Users/Aarush/Documents/Anos/Xai-governance-platform/backend/.env).
